    "body": "> so tests are imported but not used?\r\n\r\ne.g. for\r\n``` solidity\r\n// lib/dependency/src/test/ERC20.t.sol\r\ncontract MockUser {...}\r\n\r\ncontract TestERC20 {...}\r\n```\r\n```solidity\r\n// ./src/MyContract.sol\r\nimport { MockUser } from 'dependency/src/test/ERC20.t.sol'\r\n\r\ncontract MyContract {}\r\n```\r\nimporting a contract from an external test file will result in `ERC20.t.sol` to be compiled and to be included in `/out`.\r\n\r\n`forge test` seems to filter for `*.t.sol` in `/out`. So any file that lands in there will be part of the test run.\r\n\r\nThe fix would be for `forge test` to filter for the path as well.",
